1.2.2.name: wordpress/dutch-auction-masters
1.2.2.description:
This Dutch auction masters plugin enables you the ability to build your professional online auctioning website by only a few clicks. It contains 2 widgets and short tag which make you the easiest way to do it.

Dutch auction masters dedicates on making exciting online auctioning websites. For more information please visit our website: http://dutchauctionmasters.com/.

  • Demo is now available!
  • Fresh new Pro version released!

Features

DAM has following features:

1. Independent auction plug-in.
2. Real-time auction bidding process.
3. Integrated WordPress user login module. (be able to speicify which role can place bids)
4. Serveral widgets supported (List, Detail).
5. Short code supported ([List_Auction], [S
